Price is reasonable. 5 Guinness for price of $58.00. Also, 8 ft pool table is free. If you like dartslive, it is available too.
Very sincere n warm service by the crew. Good place to chill. There are 2 dartslive boards, pool table and finger food available.

Came here with two  of my colleagues once and it's quite an easygoing relaxed joint. Love that there is karaoke and pool table available. If you need entertainment that is away from town region then you can consider coming here :)
